videos.description: Anthony Davis uses a quick move to blow by Serge Ibaka and rise up for the powerful two-handed finish at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD goes baseline on Ibaka) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD goes baseline on Ibaka

videos.description: After a Lakers turnover, Ivica Zubac gets the pass on the fast break and glides to the basket to mash down a dunk for the Clippers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zubac caps fast break with powerful slam) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zubac caps fast break with powerful slam

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard blows by Wes Matthews and goes up and around Montrezl Harrell to make a sweet layup for the Clippers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kawhi swoops in for the finesse lay) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kawhi swoops in for the finesse lay

videos.description: Paul George gets the ball and quickly tries to rotate it to the corner, but doesn't realize he is actually passing it out of bounds to the referee.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Paul George turns it over passing to the ref) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paul George turns it over passing to the ref

videos.description: Kawhi Leonard drives to the basket and spins in the lane to avoid one defender then goes up and over another for the and-1 bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kawhi uses sweet spin move for and-1 bucket) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kawhi uses sweet spin move for and-1 bucket

videos.description: LeBron James gallops unchecked to the basket on the fast break and takes flight to drop the hammer on a massive dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron drops the hammer on Lakers' fast break) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron drops the hammer on Lakers' fast break

videos.description: The Lakers hold a special COVID-friendly version of a championship ring ceremony by having family, friends and other loved ones present the rings via the jumbotron.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lakers hold special championship ring ceremony on opening night) 2020/12/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lakers hold special championship ring ceremony on opening night

videos.description: LeBron James scores 22 points but it was not enough to propel the Lakers to a season-opening win as they fall to the Clippers 116-109.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (LeBron puts up 22 points in season opener vs. Clippers) 2020/12/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: LeBron puts up 22 points in season opener vs. Clippers

videos.description: The Clippers come up with a win on opening night against the Lakers for the second consecutive season, led by Paul George's 33 points as they spoil the Lakers' championship ring night.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Clippers rain on Lakers' championship ring night with 116-109 win) 2020/12/22 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Clippers rain on Lakers' championship ring night with 116-109 win

videos.description: LeBron James goes in depth on the Lakers' championship ring, including the 17 purple amethyst stones comprising the "L" on the ring's face weighing .95 carats, to represent the 95 days spent in the bubble.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (LeBron details significance of championship ring) 2020/12/22

videos.headline: LeBron details significance of championship ring
